3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper employs a local algorithm of max-min linear programs to solve the proposed task, which is an AI-related technique.
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with a distributed approach to deal with a limitation on both sensing and communication ranges, which is a systems and control-related problem.
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a local algorithm to solve the multi-robot assignment problem, which is a data structures and algorithms-related technique.
